。<br />\n就算手捉被人捉左入村！"},{"pid":"6974844afa88ac86d3f36c8477d285db7de2bac3","tid":1369963,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"880402e4211f920e52614d6bd1eb5458593617f0","tid":1369963,"uid":24425,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T00:17:49.000Z","msg":"有權 人潮管制<br />\n<br />\n利申 法律JJ"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T00:19:47.000Z","msg":"港鐵係上市公司"},{"pid":"f424aa5b16ec075a96038dc92dd08ab2686a9838","tid":1369963,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:23:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef4828cd9182db126d2334ed9e1f8760e9581ecf","tid":1369963,"uid":117679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:26:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢應該可以「要求」。但就唔一定要跟。<br />\n<br />\n即係可以要求警方入私人地方執法，但就唔可以自己走入去執法。"},{"pid":"78be2c7879b19ba572c5f91db86e38d0fb591af0","tid":1369963,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:33:15.000Z","msg":"係緊急情況之下應該做乜都得<br />\n不過事後要俾人查係咪合理去決定事件真相<br />\n而家你話開槍合理係無問題<br />\n但係唔俾人查就講唔通"},{"pid":"bb44c197dcda97596ec130f05cbb90f6f98a1532","tid":1369963,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T06:22:30.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}